---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="American Heroes — Hub" description="Mortgage programs for military, veterans, first responders, and educators. Same-day pre-approval guided by Jim Blackburn, NMLS #1072866.">
<div class="heroes-hub-scope">
<!-- ============ HERO — flag moment ============ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">★ Those who serve</span>
        <h1>You served us all. <span class="blue">Now let us</span> <span class="red">serve you home.</span></h1>
        <p class="lede">For the men and women who put service first — a mortgage process that finally puts you first.</p>
        <p class="nmls">Jim Blackburn · NMLS <b>#1072866</b> · 5.0 ★ across 624 reviews</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a href="/same-day-approval/" class="btn btn-primary">See My Options — Same-Day Pre-Approval →</a>
          <a href="/schedule-call/" class="btn btn-ghost">Talk to Our Team</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-photo">
        <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/7641906/pexels-photo-7641906.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1000&h=1200&fit=crop"
             alt="A couple receiving the keys to their new home"
             onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/1000x1200/3C3B6E/FAFAF7?text=Welcome+Home';">
        <div class="ribbon">Including those who serve in Fort Lauderdale, FL &amp; 48 states</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- trust strip -->
<div class="trust">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="stat"><span class="num">$500M+</span><span class="lab">Closed for clients</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="num">7×</span><span class="lab">Scotsman Guide Top Producer</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="num">300+</span><span class="lab">Lenders &amp; programs</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="num">5.0 ★</span><span class="lab">624 verified reviews</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="num">Same-day</span><span class="lab">Pre-approval letters</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============ ACT 1 — REVERENT ============ -->
<section class="act act-1">
  <div class="wrap act-inner">
    <div class="act-copy">
      <span class="marker"><span class="n">1</span> We honor it</span>
      <h2>Service asks everything. <em>The least a mortgage can do is respect it.</em></h2>
      <p>Long deployments. Overnight shifts. A calling that puts other people's lives ahead of your own paperwork. The work you do is not a 9-to-5, and the way you're paid rarely fits a standard underwriting box.</p>
      <p>We start by understanding what you've carried — because a lender who doesn't understand your service can't possibly understand your file.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="act-photo">
      <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/7468185/pexels-photo-7468185.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1000&h=800&fit=crop"
           alt="US Army soldier in uniform showing determination and focus"
           onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/1000x800/3C3B6E/FAFAF7?text=Those+Who+Serve';">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ ACT 2 — WARM / HUMAN ============ -->
<section class="act act-2 reverse">
  <div class="wrap act-inner">
    <div class="act-copy">
      <span class="marker"><span class="n">2</span> We see you</span>
      <h2>Behind the uniform is a person <em>who just wants to come home.</em></h2>
      <p>You're not a credit score. You're someone who wants a kitchen table for your family, a yard, a place that's yours after years of being wherever duty sent you.</p>
      <p>We treat you like the neighbor you are — real conversations, plain answers, and a team that picks up the phone. No jargon, no run-around, no making you feel like a number.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="act-photo">
      <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/17146024/pexels-photo-17146024.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1000&h=800&fit=crop"
           alt="Smiling veteran in uniform with medals, proud and warm"
           onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/1000x800/A4243B/FAFAF7?text=We+See+You';">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ ACT 3 — CONFIDENT / PREMIUM ============ -->
<section class="act act-3">
  <div class="wrap act-inner">
    <div class="act-copy">
      <span class="marker"><span class="n">3</span> You've earned this</span>
      <h2>You've earned advantages most buyers never get. <em>Let's use every one.</em></h2>
      <p>Your service may open doors others can't walk through — from VA eligibility for military families to forgivable down-payment assistance available to those who serve. The programs are real. The question is which ones fit you.</p>
      <p>Working across 300+ lenders, private banks, credit unions, and niche programs, we find the path built for your situation — then get you a same-day pre-approval so you can move with confidence.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="act-photo">
      <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/8293700/pexels-photo-8293700.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1000&h=800&fit=crop"
           alt="Happy young couple holding keys to their new home"
           onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/1000x800/B8860B/0A0E1A?text=You+Earned+This';">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ THE 10 ============ -->
<section class="roster">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="roster-head">
      <span class="eyebrow blue">★ Find your path</span>
      <h2>Built for how you serve</h2>
      <p>Every profession carries its own challenges and its own advantages. Choose yours — each page is written for the real people who do this work.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="roster-cols">
      <div class="rcol mil">
        <h3>Military &amp; Veterans <span class="tier">VA-eligible</span></h3>
        <a class="card mil" href="/american-heroes/army/"><span class="badge">★</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">US Army</span><span class="s">Active, Guard, Reserve &amp; veterans</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card mil" href="/american-heroes/navy/"><span class="badge">⚓</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">US Navy</span><span class="s">Sailors, officers &amp; veterans</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card mil" href="/american-heroes/air-force/"><span class="badge">✈</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">US Air Force</span><span class="s">Airmen, officers &amp; veterans</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card mil" href="/american-heroes/marine-corps/"><span class="badge">⬥</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">US Marine Corps</span><span class="s">Marines &amp; veterans</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card mil" href="/american-heroes/coast-guard/"><span class="badge">⚓</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">US Coast Guard</span><span class="s">Active, Reserve &amp; veterans</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card mil" href="/american-heroes/space-force/"><span class="badge">✦</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">US Space Force</span><span class="s">Guardians &amp; veterans</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="rcol civ">
        <h3>Civilian Heroes <span class="tier">Hero assistance</span></h3>
        <a class="card civ" href="/american-heroes/police-officers/"><span class="badge">⬟</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">Police Officers</span><span class="s">Sworn officers &amp; deputies</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card civ" href="/american-heroes/firefighters/"><span class="badge">▲</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">Firefighters</span><span class="s">Career &amp; volunteer</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card civ" href="/american-heroes/emt-paramedics/"><span class="badge">✚</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">EMT &amp; Paramedics</span><span class="s">Emergency medical services</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card civ" href="/american-heroes/teachers/"><span class="badge">✎</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">Teachers</span><span class="s">K-12 &amp; educators</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card civ" href="/american-heroes/corrections-officers/"><span class="badge">⬡</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">Corrections Officers</span><span class="s">Detention &amp; probation</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
        <a class="card civ" href="/american-heroes/federal-law-enforcement/"><span class="badge">★</span><span class="ct"><span class="t">Federal Law Enforcement</span><span class="s">FBI · CBP · ATF · Marshals</span></span><span class="go">›</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ DPA recognition ============ -->
<section class="dpa">
  <div class="wrap dpa-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">★ Earned, not given</span>
    <h2>There are programs that exist because of what you've done</h2>
    <p>From VA financing to forgivable down-payment assistance for those who serve, advantages may be available based on your service. We don't sell one program — we find the right fit across hundreds of options and walk you through what you qualify for.</p>
    <p class="fine">Program availability depends on your individual situation, location, and current guidelines. Let's review yours together — that conversation costs nothing.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FINAL CTA ============ -->
<section class="final">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Let's get you home.</h2>
    <p>You showed up for everyone else. Let our team show up for you — with a same-day pre-approval and a plan built around your service.</p>
    <div class="cta-row" style="justify-content:center">
      <a href="/same-day-approval/" class="btn btn-primary">See My Options →</a>
      <a href="/schedule-call/" class="btn btn-ghost">Talk to Our Team</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>

  .heroes-hub-scope{
    --ink:#0A0E1A; --ink-light:#4A5568; --ink-lighter:#6B7280;
    --paper:#FAFAF7; --paper-2:#F4F1EA; --white:#FFFFFF;
    /* premium patriotic — the ACTUAL flag colors, refined */
    --flag-red:#A4243B;      /* Old Glory red, deepened (not fire-engine) */
    --flag-red-deep:#841B2D;
    --flag-blue:#3C3B6E;     /* the real Old Glory blue, warmer than navy */
    --flag-blue-2:#2C3E73;
    --gold:#B8860B;          /* stars/medals only, sparingly */
    --border:#E5E1D8;
    --serif:'Fraunces','Iowan Old Style',Georgia,serif;
    --sans:'IBM Plex Sans',-apple-system,sans-serif;
    --mono:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,monospace;
  }
  .heroes-hub-scope *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  .heroes-hub-scope{font-family:var(--sans);background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);line-height:1.6;}
  .heroes-hub-scope img{display:block;max-width:100%;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .eyebrow{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--flag-red);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .eyebrow.blue{color:var(--flag-blue);}

  /* ====== TOP HERO — the flag moment ====== */
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero{position:relative;background:var(--paper);padding:74px 0 60px;overflow:hidden;}
  /* subtle stars-and-stripes texture, very restrained */
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:5px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--flag-red) 0 33%,var(--white) 33% 66%,var(--flag-blue) 66% 100%);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:54px;align-items:center;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:3.6rem;line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:16px 0 18px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero h1 .red{color:var(--flag-red);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero h1 .blue{color:var(--flag-blue);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero .lede{font-size:1.18rem;color:var(--ink-light);max-width:33ch;margin-bottom:26px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero .nmls{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.72rem;color:var(--ink-lighter);letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:26px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero .nmls b{color:var(--flag-blue);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .cta-row{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .btn{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:.95rem;font-weight:600;padding:14px 24px;border-radius:4px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;border:1.5px solid transparent;transition:.18s;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .btn-primary{background:var(--flag-red);color:#fff;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--flag-red-deep);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .btn-ghost{border-color:var(--flag-blue);color:var(--flag-blue);background:transparent;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .btn-ghost:hover{background:var(--flag-blue);color:#fff;}
  /* hero image — real service person photo slot */
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero-photo{position:relative;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:4/4.4;background:#dcd8cf;box-shadow:0 24px 60px -28px rgba(60,59,110,.5);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero-photo img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:50% 30%;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .hero-photo .ribbon{position:absolute;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#fff;
    background:linear-gradient(0deg,rgba(10,14,26,.82),transparent);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .stars{color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:2px;}

  /* trust strip */
  .heroes-hub-scope .trust{border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--white);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .trust .wrap{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:30px;justify-content:space-between;padding:20px 32px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .trust .stat{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .trust .num{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--flag-blue);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .trust .lab{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-lighter);}

  /* ====== THREE-ACT EMOTIONAL ARC ====== */
  .heroes-hub-scope .act{padding:78px 0;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:50px;align-items:center;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act.reverse .act-inner{direction:rtl;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act.reverse .act-copy{direction:ltr;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-photo{border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:5/4;background:#dcd8cf;box-shadow:0 18px 44px -26px rgba(10,14,26,.4);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-photo img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:2.3rem;line-height:1.1;margin:14px 0 16px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act p{font-size:1.08rem;color:var(--ink-light);margin-bottom:14px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act .marker{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.66rem;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-lighter);margin-bottom:4px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act .marker .n{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.7rem;color:#fff;}
  /* act 1 reverent (blue), act 2 warm (red), act 3 confident (gold-rule) */
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-1{background:var(--paper);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-1 .marker .n{background:var(--flag-blue);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-1 h2 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--flag-blue);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-2{background:var(--paper-2);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-2 .marker .n{background:var(--flag-red);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-2 h2 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--flag-red);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-3{background:var(--flag-blue);color:#fff;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-3 .marker{color:#c9c8e0;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-3 .marker .n{background:var(--gold);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-3 h2{color:#fff;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-3 h2 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--gold);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-3 p{color:#d6d5e6;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .act-3 .act-photo{box-shadow:0 18px 44px -22px rgba(0,0,0,.6);}

  /* ====== THE 10 — two columns Military / Civilian ====== */
  .heroes-hub-scope .roster{padding:84px 0;background:var(--white);border-top:1px solid var(--border);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .roster-head{text-align:center;max-width:60ch;margin:0 auto 48px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .roster-head h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:2.4rem;margin:12px 0 12px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .roster-head p{color:var(--ink-light);font-size:1.08rem;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .roster-cols{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:44px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .rcol h3{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.74rem;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;
    padding-bottom:12px;margin-bottom:8px;border-bottom:2px solid;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .rcol.mil h3{color:var(--flag-blue);border-color:var(--flag-blue);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .rcol.civ h3{color:var(--flag-red);border-color:var(--flag-red);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .rcol h3 .tier{font-size:.6rem;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;letter-spacing:.06em;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .rcol.mil .tier{background:#3C3B6E18;color:var(--flag-blue);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .rcol.civ .tier{background:#A4243B18;color:var(--flag-red);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .card{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:15px 14px;border-radius:5px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink);transition:.15s;border:1px solid transparent;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .card:hover{background:var(--paper-2);border-color:var(--border);transform:translateX(3px);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .card .badge{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:7px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.05rem;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .mil .badge{background:#3C3B6E14;color:var(--flag-blue);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .civ .badge{background:#A4243B14;color:var(--flag-red);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .card .ct{flex:1;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .card .ct .t{font-weight:600;font-size:1.02rem;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .card .ct .s{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--ink-lighter);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .card .go{color:var(--ink-lighter);font-size:.9rem;}

  /* ====== DPA recognition band ====== */
  .heroes-hub-scope .dpa{padding:64px 0;background:var(--paper-2);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .dpa-inner{max-width:74ch;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .dpa h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:2rem;margin:12px 0 14px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .dpa p{color:var(--ink-light);font-size:1.08rem;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .dpa .fine{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--ink-lighter);margin-top:18px;font-style:italic;}

  /* ====== FINAL CTA ====== */
  .heroes-hub-scope .final{padding:0;background:var(--flag-red);color:#fff;position:relative;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .final::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:5px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--flag-blue) 0 33%,var(--white) 33% 66%,var(--flag-red-deep) 66% 100%);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .final .wrap{padding:64px 32px;text-align:center;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .final h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:600;font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:14px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .final p{font-size:1.12rem;color:#f6e3e6;max-width:52ch;margin:0 auto 26px;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .final .btn-primary{background:#fff;color:var(--flag-red);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .final .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--paper-2);}
  .heroes-hub-scope .final .btn-ghost{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);color:#fff;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .final .btn-ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.14);}

  .heroes-hub-scope .footnote{background:var(--ink);color:#8b93a7;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.68rem;letter-spacing:.03em;padding:18px 32px;text-align:center;}
  .heroes-hub-scope .footnote b{color:#c9d0de;}

  @media(max-width:860px){
    .heroes-hub-scope .hero-grid,.heroes-hub-scope .act-inner,.heroes-hub-scope .roster-cols{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .heroes-hub-scope .hero h1{font-size:2.6rem;}
    .heroes-hub-scope .act.reverse .act-inner{direction:ltr;}
  }
  /* placeholder photo styling */
  .heroes-hub-scope .ph{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:100%;height:100%;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,#e8e4da,#e8e4da 12px,#e1ddd2 12px,#e1ddd2 24px);
    color:#a39d8f;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.68rem;text-align:center;letter-spacing:.05em;padding:20px;}

</style>
